name: JW PEI Women's Joy Shoulder Bag
reviews: 1. Bought this from Amazon for better return policy (on their website they don't allow any return/exchanges in discounted/sale items) and $120 for free delivery.  So prime for the win.2. The purse itself looks very well made. Looks very classy and as my husband said "very old money, like you have enough money that you dont show it off with a LV bag vibe". The best thing is if can be crossbody/shoulder depending on the trend or style.3. With everyday use, I don't think it will last more than 2 years. But occasional careful use, I think it will last me a really long time (I used to live a hotter area, have realized that vegan leather last much longer in colder areas than hotter)4. It smelt really weird when in the box. A few minutes of airing it out, the smell disappeared.5. Came with a dust bag for better storage.I would say the make is right there with Charles and Keith/ Calvin Klein vegan/faux leather bags.I don't use leather so this is perfect.
